file.name: NotificationResponse.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
NotificationResponse:
  type: object
  description: |
    Notification response. Contains the result of a processed notification.
  properties:
    id:
      type: string
      description: |
        Notification id which indicates that the notification was processed successfully.
    trace:
      $ref: "./TraceResponse.yaml#/TraceResponse"
